[00:00] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'Hi, my name is Michael. I\'m the CEO and founder of Hedra. &gt;&gt; And I\'m Russ, CEO and co-founder of LiveKit. &gt;&gt; Today, we\'re excited to announce the Hedra Live avatar in partnership with our friends at LiveKit. &gt;&gt; Large language models have changed the'

[00:12] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'world. We now have super smart computers that can do everything from coding to customer support. And in the last year, voice has emerged as a default interface for interacting with AI. We believe'

[00:26] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'video is the next unlock for bringing even richer interactions with voice agents. But generative video has historically been high latency and expensive. That\'s why today we\'re partnering with LiveKit, the leader in'

[00:38] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'voice and video AI infrastructure to launch Hedra Live avatars. We\'ve integrated Hedra Live avatars into LiveKit\'s agents framework. With a few lines of code, you can give any AI model'

[00:50] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'a visual identity streaming over Live Kit\'s global network with less than 100 milliseconds of latency. &gt;&gt; How can I help you today? You\'re doing the best you can. We can talk through what\'s going on.'

[01:03] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: '&gt;&gt; The Hedra avatar is different in three key ways. One, cost. Our real-time model is up to 15 times cheaper than existing solutions, so you can focus your budget on users, not servers. Two, latency. We\'re designed for true realtime use.'

[01:18] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'Every frame is generated on demand at record price performance. Once I have that information, I can look into arranging a replacement or refund or any other alternative that I can find. And'

[01:30] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'three, flexibility. Future Live avatars require only a single starting image and work across photorealistic, animated, and even animal characters. To celebrate this launch, we\'ve built a series of'

[01:42] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'demos to show you how fast it is to get started with LiveKit and Hedra. Bring your own LLM and text to speech model. Plug it in directly to Hedra and LiveKit. We\'re compatible with category'

[01:54] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'leading voice models like the latest 11 Labs 2.5 Flash. We believe that the next wave of consumer and enterprise applications will leverage not just real-time voice, but real time video.'

[02:06] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'And we\'re excited to partner with Hedra to help you build it. Hedra avatars are available today to build with at hedra.com/real time. We\'re pricing at 5 cents a minute'

[02:18] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'with no annual contract or commitment, just video on demand.'
